<br><center><p><b> RESTAURANT MANAGER </b>
<br><br><b>Apply Online Today!</b>
<br><a href="https://re31.ultipro.com/MIL1018/JobBoard//JobDetails.aspx?__ID=*B59409F500607116" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://mwartwork.com/ads/millers/Apply-Now-A.jpg"></a><br>
<hr></hr>

<br><b>Three Locations in the Chicago Area: Lombard, Chicago Ridge &amp; North Riverside
<br>Opening in Norridge April 2017</b></center><br>

<hr></hr>
<p> We don't need just a manager. We need you. Because calling this a manager job doesn't really do it justice. It's bigger than that. Much bigger.<br><br>
<b>Miller's Ale House</b> started out as a local place where friends and families got together for great food, good laughs and big games. People loved that place so much, we opened another, and then another. <br>
There's a vibe here that you can't quite explain, but you know it's there. And that's why we need more than a manager. Someone who gets what's special about this place. Someone who wants to be a valued contributor to our culture and help us grow something much more valuable than a balance sheet (but yes, we want to grow that too). Someone who understands how to motivate others to get the work done, and shares our belief on how to work hard and lead a good life. If this sounds like you, come join the amazing, community-oriented team at Miller's Ale House.

<br><br><b> WHAT ARE THE PERKS?</b>
<ul><li>Highly competitive compensation package  
<li>Medical, dental &amp; vision 
<li>401K with company match 
<li>Attainable quarterly bonus 
<li>Bi-Annual performance appraisals with the opportunity for an annual merit increase 
<li>Dining privileges for the manager &amp; immediate family 
<li>Employer paid short term disability &amp; life insurance
<li>Employee assistance programs
<li>Pet insurance </ul>

<br><b> HOW DO WE MAKE WORK/LIFE BALANCE A REALITY?</b>
<ul><li>Five-day work week  
<li>Maximum of 3 closing shifts per week 
<li>Manager schedule written a month in advance 
<li>One paid time off day per quarter 
<li>One week of paid vacation every 6 months, starting day one </ul>

<br><b>Hours of Operation: 11am-2am (at most locations), 7 days a week

<p></b>Miller's Ale House is an Equal Opportunity and e-Verify employer and all qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, national origin, disability status, protected veteran status, or any other characteristic protected by law.</p></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></p></p>    </section>

